fields.name: DnsServiceIP
fields.description: An IP address assigned to the Kubernetes DNS service. It must be within the Kubernetes service address range specified in serviceCidr.

fields.name: DockerBridgeCidr
fields.description: A CIDR notation IP range assigned to the Docker bridge network. It must not overlap with any Subnet IP ranges or the Kubernetes service address range.

fields.name: ServiceCidr
fields.description: A CIDR notation IP range from which to assign service cluster IPs. It must not overlap with any Subnet IP ranges.

fields.name: SubnetId
fields.description: Virtual network subnet resource ID the compute nodes belong to
